node.text: So much fun on my latest trip. This was at @bobclarkreptiles and a giant Retic!! I’m so happy to be home but i miss the adventures from the road. Always push your comfort zone. Your personal growth always comes in making the uncomfortable comfortable… #reticulatedpython #giantsnake #retic #python #adventure #travel #wildanimals #snakes #reptiles #brianbarcyzk
